import React,{useState, useEffect} from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import '../../css/navcss.css' import { getPKH } from '../../utils/wallet' export default function Navigation() { const [profile,setProfile] = useState(false); useEffect(()=>{ const getaccount=async()=>{ const res = await getPKH(); if(res != ''){ setProfile(true) } } getaccount(); }) return (
    Home { profile?( View NFT ):"" } Mint NFT About Us Roadmap
) }
